'''蕾貝卡·霍爾'''（{{lang-en|Rebecca Hall}}，{{bd|1982年|5月3日|catIdx=H}}），[[英國|英國]]女演員暨導演。

霍爾的出道作是在1992年，年僅九歲時參演的英國[[電視連續劇|電視連續劇]]《{{le|園丁女偵探|The Camomile Lawn (TV serial)}}》<ref name=hall>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/3900390/Hall-of-fame-Rebecca-Hall.html|title=Hall of fame: Rebecca Hall|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=23 December 2008|access-date=22 July 2017|archive-date=2021-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210912080132/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/3900390/Hall-of-fame-Rebecca-Hall.html}}</ref>，由她的父親{{le|彼得·霍爾|Peter Hall (director)}}執導，劇本是改編自{{le|瑪麗·韋斯利|Mary Wesley}}的同名小說，[[第四台_(英國)|第四台]]電視台製作。霍爾的[[舞台劇|舞台劇]]處女作也是由父親經手，即為2002年推出的《{{le|華倫夫人的職業|Mrs. Warren's Profession}}》，原作為[[蕭伯納|蕭伯納]]，霍爾在劇中扮演華倫夫人的女兒，並一舉摘下英國{{le|伊恩·查爾森獎|Ian Charleson Awards}}首獎。此獎旨在肯定英國三十歲以內的舞台劇演員，獲獎當時，霍爾年僅二十歲。

2006年，霍爾首次登上大銀幕，和[[詹姆斯·麥艾維|詹姆斯·麥艾維]]合作演出[[浪漫喜劇|浪漫喜劇]]《[[戀愛學分|戀愛學分]]》後，隨即參演[[克里斯多福·諾蘭|克里斯多福·諾蘭]]執導的[[驚悚片|驚悚片]]《[[頂尖對決|頂尖對決]]》。2008年，霍爾在[[伍迪·艾倫|伍迪·艾倫]]執導的浪漫喜劇《[[情遇巴塞隆納|情遇巴塞隆納]]》中擔綱女主角並入圍多項獎項提名，如[[金球獎|金球獎]]的最佳女主角<ref name="GQ">{{cite news|url=https://www.gq.com/women/photos/201004/rebecca-hall-actress-photos-vicky-cristina-barcelona|title=Rated 'R' for Rebecca|last=Nugent|first=Benjamin|date=30 April 2010|work=gq|access-date=8 October 2010|archive-date=2010-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100510082347/http://www.gq.com/women/photos/201004/rebecca-hall-actress-photos-vicky-cristina-barcelona}}</ref>；該片最後拿下美國[[哥譚獨立電影獎|哥譚獨立電影獎]]的{{le|最佳群戲獎|Best Ensemble Cast}}。

霍爾的戲路甚廣，曾參演各類戲劇電影，如[[朗·霍華|朗·霍華]]執導的歷史[[劇情片|劇情片]]《[[請問總統先生|請問總統先生]]》、[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]自編自導自演的[[犯罪片|犯罪]]驚悚片《[[竊盜城|竊盜城]]》<ref name="GQ" />、和[[多明尼克·魏斯特|多明尼克·魏斯特]]合演恐怖驚悚片《{{le|靈動檔案|The Awakening (2011 film)}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37497/its-time-studiocanals-awakening|title=It's Time for StudioCanal's Awakening|work=Dread Central|date=16 September 2012|access-date=2021-09-12|archive-date=2012-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013164318/http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37497/its-time-studiocanals-awakening}}</ref><ref>[http://press.optimumreleasing.net/press/?id=1457 Optimum Releasing website.] {{Wayback|url=http://press.optimumreleasing.net/press/?id=1457 |date=20160426211913 }}. Retrieved 19 August 2011</ref>、超級英雄片《[[鋼鐵人3|鋼鐵人3]]》、和[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]攜手演出[[科幻電影|科幻片]]《[[全面進化|全面進化]]》、和[[傑森·貝特曼|傑森·貝特曼]]合作心理驚悚片《[[非禮勿弒|非禮勿弒]]》，以及和[[路克·伊凡斯|路克·伊凡斯]]搭檔演出傳記劇情片《[[神力女超人的秘密|神力女超人的秘密]]》，還有怪獸片《[[哥吉拉大戰金剛|哥吉拉大戰金剛]]》。2016年，霍爾在傳記式劇情片《{{le|直播自殺事件|Christine (2016 film)}}》中詮釋女記者[[克莉絲汀·查伯克|克莉絲汀·查伯克]]，霍爾的精湛演技廣受影評盛讚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/jan/24/christine-review-rebecca-hall-astonishes-in-real-life-horror-story|title=Christine review: Rebecca Hall astonishes in real-life horror story|website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|first=Nigel|last=M. Smith|date=24 January 2016|accessdate=25 September 2016|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114141916/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/jan/24/christine-review-rebecca-hall-astonishes-in-real-life-horror-story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/christine-review-1201687262/|title=Sundance Film Review: 'Christine'|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Guy|last=Lodge|date=24 January 2016|access-date=22 July 2017|archive-date=2022-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220311093434/https://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/christine-review-1201687262/}}</ref>。

霍爾也致力於參演英國電視劇，並取得了不俗的成績，例如英國第四台推出的迷你劇集《{{le|血色迷宮:1974|Red Riding#Red Riding 1974}}》中，她和[[安德魯·加菲爾德|安德魯·加菲爾德]]與[[西恩·賓|西恩·賓]]合作，抱回了2010年[[英國電視學院獎|英國電視學院獎]]的最佳女配角獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/awards-database.html?sq=Rebecca+Hall|title=Awards Database – The BAFTA site|publisher=Bafta.org|access-date=8 May 2011|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105084017/http://www.bafta.org/awards-database.html?sq=Rebecca+Hall}}</ref> 。2013年，霍爾參演《[[一戰往事|榮耀之盡]]》，和[[班奈狄克·康柏拜區|班奈狄克·康柏拜區]]有精彩對手戲，讓她奪得了英國電視學院獎的最佳女主角獎，本劇由[[英國廣播公司第二台|英國廣播公司第二台]]和美國[[HBO|HBO]]、[[比利時|比利時]][[VRT|VRT]]三者合作出品<ref>{{Cite web|title=BAFTA Awards Search {{!}} BAFTA Awards|url=http://awards.bafta.org/keyword-search?keywords=Rebecca+Hall|access-date=2021-09-08|website=awards.bafta.org|archive-date=2022-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328102446/http://awards.bafta.org/keyword-search?keywords=Rebecca+Hall}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/10047416/Baftas-2013-the-contenders.html|title=Baftas 2013: the contenders|last=O'Donovan|first=Gerard|date=10 May 2013|work=The Daily Telegraph|access-date=23 July 2017|archive-date=2021-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210912082522/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/10047416/Baftas-2013-the-contenders.html}}</ref> 。

2021年，霍爾推出她首度執導之作《{{le|白色通行證|Passing (film)}}》，獲得不少影評好評<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-31|title=Passing review – Rebecca Hall's elegant but inert directorial debut|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/jan/31/passing-review-rebecca-halls-elegant-but-inert-directorial-debut|access-date=2021-09-08|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220526105028/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/jan/31/passing-review-rebecca-halls-elegant-but-inert-directorial-debut}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-29|title='Passing' explores the complications of biracial identity. For Rebecca Hall, it's personal.|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-01-29/rebecca-hall-passing-sundance|url-status=live|access-date=2021-09-08|website=Los Angeles Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220525222954/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2021-01-29/rebecca-hall-passing-sundance}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Rao|first=Mallika|date=2021-09-01|title=‘Imagine a Black Woman Just Wanting Something’|url=https://www.vulture.com/article/ruth-negga-passing.html|access-date=2021-09-08|website=Vulture|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124163935/https://www.vulture.com/article/ruth-negga-passing.html}}</ref>。

