== 私人生活 ==
1982年，霍爾生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]<ref name=birth>''Births, Marriages & Deaths Index of England & Wales, 1916–2005.'' Gives name at birth as "Rebecca Maria Hall".</ref>，家人幾乎都從事表演事業，父親{{le|彼得·霍爾}}是英國舞台劇[[導演|導演]]暨[[皇家莎士比亞劇團|皇家莎士比亞劇團]]創辦人，母親{{le|瑪麗亞·艾文|}}是[[美國|美國]][[歌劇|歌劇]]演唱家，擁有多種血統如[[非洲|非]]裔、[[德國|德]]裔、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]裔以及[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]裔等<ref name=cbl>{{Cite news|last=Hattenstone|first=Simon|title=Who, me? Why everyone is talking about Rebecca Hall|work=The Guardian|date=12 June 2010|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/jun/12/rebecca-hall-interview|accessdate=27 September 2010|location=London|archive-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620074229/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/jun/12/rebecca-hall-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ref1">{{cite news|last=Isenberg|first=Barbara|title=MUSIC No-Risk Opera? Not Even Close Maria Ewing, one of the most celebrated sopranos in opera, leaps again into the role of Tosca, keeping alive her streak of acclaimed performances while remaining true to herself|work=Los Angeles Times|date=8 November 1992|url=https://articles.latimes.com/1992-11-08/entertainment/ca-1_1_maria-ewing|accessdate=8 May 2011|archive-date=2017-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525115323/http://articles.latimes.com/1992-11-08/entertainment/ca-1_1_maria-ewing|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ref2">{{cite news|last=McLellan|first=Joseph|title=Article: Extra-Sensuous Perception;Soprano Maria Ewing, a Steamy 'Salome'|work=The Washington Post|date=15 November 1990|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1158782.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022180005/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1158782.html|archive-date=2012-10-22|accessdate=6 February 2010|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="ref3">{{cite news|last=Marsh|first=Robert C.|title=Growth of Maria Ewing continues with 'Salome' // Role of princess proves crowning achievement|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=18 December 1988|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-3919649.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022180018/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-3919649.html|archive-date=2012-10-22|accessdate=6 February 2010|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，雙親在她年幼時便分居，1990年離異<ref name=cbl />。霍爾有五位同父異母的手足，大哥{{le|克里斯多福·霍爾|Christopher Hall|克里斯多福}}是英國電視劇[[製片人|製片人]]，大姊{{le|珍妮佛·霍爾|Jennifer Caron Hall|珍妮佛}}是女演員、[[詞曲作家|詞曲作家]]、[[藝術家|藝術家]]暨[[記者|記者]]，二哥{{le|愛德華·霍爾|Edward Hall|愛德華}}是英國舞台劇及電影導演，並經營{{le|普羅派拉|Propeller (theatre company)}}劇團，該團皆為男性，專司演出[[莎士比亞|莎士比亞]]的作品。還有二姊露西（{{lang-en|Lucy Hall}}）和妹妹艾瑪（{{lang-en|Emma Hall}}），六人都在父親執導或製作的作品中粉墨登場過<ref name=cbl /><ref>{{cite news|first=Ginny|last=Dougary|title=The conversation: Peter Hall|work=The Times|date=4 April 2009}}</ref>。

霍爾曾就讀[[東薩塞克斯郡|東薩塞克斯郡]][[布萊頓|布萊頓]]的{{le|羅丁女子中學|Roedean School}}，在學時曾任{{le|學生代表|Head girl and head boy}}<ref name=cbl />。她隨後進入[[劍橋大學聖凱薩琳學院|劍橋大學聖凱薩琳學院]]攻讀[[英語文學|英語文學]]，但在畢業前一年輟學<ref name="cbl" /><ref>{{cite news|title=Former Cambridge student takes her first leading role|url=http://www.tcs.cam.ac.uk/download/TCS_Volume13_Michaelmas_Issue6.pdf|publisher=[[The_Cambridge_Student|The Cambridge Student]]|date=3 November 2011|page=06}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.signonsandiego.com/uniontrib/20050220/news_1a20rebecca.html|title=For Rebecca Hall, it's all in the family business|last=Farber|first=Jim|date=20 February 2005|work=[[U-T_San_Diego|U-T San Diego]]|accessdate=8 May 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101222031059/http://www.signonsandiego.com/uniontrib/20050220/news_1a20rebecca.html|archivedate=2010-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍爾在校期間非常熱衷於學生劇團活動，甚至還創立了自己的劇團<ref name=prestigenotes>{{cite web|url=http://media.movieweb.com/galleries/3728/notes.pdf|title=''The Prestige'' production notes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930212132/http://media.movieweb.com/galleries/3728/notes.pdf|archivedate=2007-09-30|accessdate=9 November 2006|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。她也是[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]舞台劇社團{{le|馬羅社|The Marlowe Society}}成員，與[[丹·史蒂文斯|丹·史蒂文斯]]攜手合作過不少作品，後者當時就讀於[[劍橋大學伊曼紐爾學院|劍橋大學伊曼紐爾學院]]的英語文學系<ref>{{cite news|title=Macbeth|url=http://www.societies.cam.ac.uk/marlowe/showarchive/macbeth/press.htm|publisher=[[Marlowe_Society|Marlowe Society]]|year=2002|accessdate=2020-09-16|archive-date=2012-12-23|archive-url=https://archive.is/20121223112051/http://www.societies.cam.ac.uk/marlowe/showarchive/macbeth/press.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Rebecca Hall takes the lead|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/8852878/Rebecca-Hall-takes-the-lead.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111029142805/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/8852878/Rebecca-Hall-takes-the-lead.html|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=29 October 2011|archivedate=2011-10-29|accessdate=2020-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。霍爾後來也為丹的女兒維珞（英語：Willow）擔任教母<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/arts/film/article4196587.ece|title=Downton Abbey’s Dan Stevens goes to Hollywood|work=[[The_Times|The Times]]|date=6 September 2014|accessdate=2020-09-16|archive-date=2016-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105063227/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/arts/film/article4196587.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

